Sure, here are ten objects that are commonly associated with Jollibee:

1. Jollibee mascot costume
2. Chickenjoy (Jollibee's famous fried chicken)
3. Yumburger (Jollibee's signature burger)
4. Jolly Spaghetti
5. Peach Mango Pie
6. Jollibee toys (given with kids' meals)
7. Jollibee party hats
8. Jollibee tumblers and cups
9. Jollibee balloons
10. Jollibee food containers and packaging
